Text: Cc I had a very successful meeting with Michael Capellas this morning Once again I want to thank you for making this relationship possible Michael mentioned to me that the two of you are expected to meet this afternoon The following is an outline of my discussion points with Michael CYNET Progress Report CYNET Business Plan CYNETs Bundled Solution Convergent Messaging iPAQ Expansion PackCYPAQ wireless modem and CYNET dialer software Technology Demonstration Funding Discussion Million We are pleased to report that the relationship between CYNET and Compaq is growing See attached excerpts from todays meeting If you have any questions feel free to call me Vincent W Beale Ken Layppt Ken Layppt
